snippet.title: Animal Online Games Animal Doctor Games - Cute Pet Hospital Game
snippet.description:
Animal Online Games Animal Doctor Games - Cute Pet Hospital Game .Click your cute pet patients to pick them up. Take them to the correct room with a blue door to diagnose them, and to the correct room with a green door to cure their ailments. If you need help, just ask Nurse Chloe. Good luck, doctor!
Play Animal Doctor Games Online Here
http://www.girlsgogames.com/game/cute_pet_hospital.html
